I"z<p>This is because sshd has registered too many logins with the incorrect password.<br />
To reset the incorrect password count, run the following command:</p>
<pre>pam_tally2 --&lt;user&gt; --reset</pre>
<p>This is configured under /etc/pam.d/sshd</p>
